rComments: During lectures I wanted to die. He understands what he's talking about, but he's just so boring. However this class is really easy. There is no final, just a final [and only] paper. The midterm, and pop quizzes are open notes/book. Even though I don't want to admit I learned anything because the class was so boring, I did. Easy but boring GenEd

Very boring, grades oddly.  He didn't seem to understand what I was saying in my papers sometimes, but I've never had this problem with other teachers.  Don't bother reading the book, but use it for open-book tests and quizzes cuz you will need it!!!  The class kind of depends on who your TA is.
